So long as a servant was present, no other words passed between them. No, no, no, said the uncle, pleasantly. Thank you, said the Marquis--very sweetly indeed. In effect, sir, pursued the nephew, I believe it to be at once your
bad fortune, and my good fortune, that has kept me out of a prison in
France here. His tone lingered in the air, almost like the tone of a musical
instrument.